folder: Van Brunt St. & President St., Brooklyn, NY
original_title: Brooklyn: Van Brunt St. - President St.
text:
Van Brunt Street (right), east side, south of President Street; viewed across the S.W. corner. Also shown is President Street, south side, east from
Van Brunt to Columbia Streets.
March 27, 1937.
P. L. Sperr.
